<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 15:12:35 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>美国旅游业等待中国旅游业创2019年新高</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/us-travel-sector-faces-long-wait-china-tourism-hit-2019-highs-2024-04-22/</link><description>由于中国经济增长缓慢和成本高昂，导致游客远离美国，美国旅游业至少还需要等待两年，利润丰厚的中国旅游业才能恢复到疫情前的水平。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 12:28:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/us-travel-sector-faces-long-wait-china-tourism-hit-2019-highs-2024-04-22/</guid></item><item><title>特斯拉股价因盈利前降价而暴跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-shares-drop-price-cuts-run-up-earnings-2024-04-22/</link><description>特斯拉周一暴跌 4%，其最新的全球降价举措引发了华尔街对这家电动汽车制造商在本周晚些时候发布财报之前利润率下降的担忧。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 12:03:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-shares-drop-price-cuts-run-up-earnings-2024-04-22/</guid></item><item><title>英国警方指控两名男子为中国从事间谍活动</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/uk-prosecutors-authorise-charges-against-two-men-over-spying-china-2024-04-22/</link><description>英国警方周一指控两名男子为中国从事间谍活动，其中一名男子据称曾在英国议会为执政的保守党一位著名议员担任研究员。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 11:47:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/uk-prosecutors-authorise-charges-against-two-men-over-spying-china-2024-04-22/</guid></item><item><title>由于主要市场疲软，印度成品钻石出口下降 27.5%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/indias-polished-diamond-exports-drop-275-key-markets-falter-2024-04-22/</link><description>一家主要贸易机构周一表示，由于美国、中国和阿联酋的需求低迷，印度 2023/24 年切割和成品钻石出口额同比下降 27.5%，至 159.7 亿美元。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 11:38:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/indias-polished-diamond-exports-drop-275-key-markets-falter-2024-04-22/</guid></item><item><title>无聊的统治？霍纳为“节拍器”维斯塔潘辩护</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/formula1/boring-dominance-horner-defends-metronome-verstappen-2024-04-22/</link><description>红牛主帅克里斯蒂安·霍纳否认了马克斯·维斯塔潘让一级方程式赛车变得无聊的说法，这位三届世界冠军周末在中国将自己的统治力提升到了新的高度。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 11:30:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/formula1/boring-dominance-horner-defends-metronome-verstappen-2024-04-22/</guid></item><item><title>早间竞价：随着第一季度的到来，大型科技公司陷入困境，英伟达惨遭重创</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-04-22/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 10:07:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-04-22/</guid></item><item><title>减税政策承压 中国一季度财政收入下降</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-q1-fiscal-revenue-falls-tax-cut-policies-weigh-2024-04-22/</link><description>财政部周一表示，受前期减税政策等特殊因素影响，一季度财政收入同比下降2.3%。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 09:05:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-q1-fiscal-revenue-falls-tax-cut-policies-weigh-2024-04-22/</guid></item><item><title>德国逮捕三名涉嫌向中国提供技术的人</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/germany-arrests-three-suspected-spying-china-2024-04-22/</link><description>德国官员周一表示，三名德国人因涉嫌与中国特勤局合作移交可用于军事目的的技术而被捕，这些技术可能有助于加强中国海军。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 08:29:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/germany-arrests-three-suspected-spying-china-2024-04-22/</guid></item><item><title>中国反对日本首相参拜靖国神社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-opposes-japan-prime-ministers-offering-yasukuni-shrine-2024-04-22/</link><description>中国周一对日本首相岸田文雄在东京一座有争议的神社进行祭祀表示强烈反对，中国和韩国认为该神社是日本过去军事侵略的象征。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 08:12:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-opposes-japan-prime-ministers-offering-yasukuni-shrine-2024-04-22/</guid></item><item><title>中国梦的破灭迫使西方金融公司削减成本</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/souring-china-dreams-force-western-financial-firms-cut-costs-2024-04-22/</link><description>就在几年前，中国经济蓬勃发展带来的利润丰厚的商业前景导致西方金融公司（从投资银行到资产管理）竞相扩大业务范围并从世界各地招募人才。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 07:42:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/souring-china-dreams-force-western-financial-firms-cut-costs-2024-04-22/</guid></item><item><title>小米CEO称将在车展上介绍SU7产能及交付计划</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/xiaomi-ceo-says-will-introduce-production-capacity-delivery-plan-su7-auto-show-2024-04-22/</link><description>周一，小米首席执行官表示，该公司将在北京车展上提供有关 SU7 产能和交付计划的更多细节。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 07:13:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/xiaomi-ceo-says-will-introduce-production-capacity-delivery-plan-su7-auto-show-2024-04-22/</guid></item><item><title>中国国家规划师警告电动汽车价格战加剧供应过剩</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/prices-evs-plug-in-hybrids-fall-chinese-city-shenzhen-state-planner-says-2024-04-22/</link><description>中国国家规划部门周一在一份声明中表示，由于供应过剩等问题，预计今年电动汽车和插电式混合动力汽车制造商之间的价格战将会加剧。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 07:09:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/prices-evs-plug-in-hybrids-fall-chinese-city-shenzhen-state-planner-says-2024-04-22/</guid></item><item><title>国际象棋印度少年古克什赢得候选人赛，与丁丁对决</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/chess-indian-teenager-gukesh-wins-candidates-sets-up-ding-showdown-2024-04-22/</link><description>周日在多伦多举行的双循环赛最后一天，古克什·多玛拉朱 (Gukesh Dommaraju) 与中村光 (Hikaru Nakamura) 战平，成为赢得男子国际象棋候选锦标赛最年轻的选手。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 07:03:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/chess-indian-teenager-gukesh-wins-candidates-sets-up-ding-showdown-2024-04-22/</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯诺镍公司计划在中国建铜厂，距离最大买家更近</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/russias-nornickel-move-copper-plant-china-ceo-tells-interfax-2024-04-22/</link><description>诺镍公司周一表示，由于难以向遭受制裁的俄罗斯进口设备，该公司将关闭其北极铜厂，并与一位未透露姓名的合作伙伴在中国建造一座工厂，以直接进入全球最大的金属市场。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 06:46:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/russias-nornickel-move-copper-plant-china-ceo-tells-interfax-2024-04-22/</guid></item><item><title>智库 SIPRI 称，2023 年全球军费开支因冲突而增长 7%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/growth-global-military-spending-accelerated-2023-think-tank-sipri-says-2024-04-22/</link><description>一家领先智库周一表示，随着国际和平与安全恶化，2023 年全球军费开支增长 7%，达到 2.43 万亿美元，这是自 2009 年以来的最大年度增幅。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 06:46:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/growth-global-military-spending-accelerated-2023-think-tank-sipri-says-2024-04-22/</guid></item></channel></rss>